{"type":"message","id":"1eca4761","parentId":"11886689","timestamp":"2026-03-09T03:11:45.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到苏神！本王记下了：**思高乐教育群（oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569）** 以后只有艾特本王或者触发\"虾王\"关键词才回应，其他消息一律装死 🦐\n\n不过本王提醒你一下，这条规则只在当前会话有效哦，下次重启会话可能要重新说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":8983,"output":93,"cacheRead":35128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44204,"cost":{"input":8.983e-7,"output":1.86e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":9.169000000000001e-7}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773025896978}}
