 should keep my answer concise and mention that both the cron and git backup are fine, but the baseline file is broken due to a checksum error.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 心跳测了，结果如下：\n\n- `nightly-security-audit`：正常，**3 小时前**跑过\n- `git-backup-daily`：正常，**3 小时前**跑过\n- Git 最近一次提交：**2026-03-09 10:24:03 +0800**\n- 但是有个小问题：**安全基线校验失败了**\n\n具体原因不是配置一定被改坏了，而是你这个基线文件 `~/.openclaw/.config-baseline.sha256` 里写的是相对路径：\n\n`openclaw.json`\n\n所以从当前目录执行 `shasum -a 256 -c ~/.openclaw/.config-baseline.sha256` 时，会去当前目录找 `openclaw.json`，结果找不到，就报：\n\n`openclaw.json: FAILED open or read`\n\n也就是说，**更像是校验文件路径写法有问题，不一定是真异常**。\n\n你要的话，本王下一步可以直接帮你：\n1. 定位真正该校验的 `openclaw.json`\n2. 把基线文件改成绝对路径\n3. 再重跑一次心跳校验\n\n这次测试结论一句话：**cron 正常，备份正常，基线校验脚本有路径坑。** 🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae53ddb4048191a19a8fab8c6caf7b"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":187,"output":579,"cacheRead":43904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44670,"cost":{"input":0.00032725,"output":0.008106,"cacheRead":0.007683199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016116449999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773032401736}}
