his well. I want to communicate this clearly and concisely, so the user understands the situation while also considering how we might improve the upload experience in the future. It’s important to make sure I'm expressing this effectively!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 果然，这次工具链又卡了。\n\n本王刚刚按语音方式重发了一次，但飞书返回的是：\n**Media upload failed (400)**，结果又退化成了**文字链接**，不是可播放语音条。\n\n结论很明确：\n**本王现在手头这套直连工具，还不能稳定把语音条正确发到你飞书里。**\n要真发成飞书可播放语音，还是得走我记忆里那套：\n- 先准备 **opus**\n- 再拿到 **file_key**\n- 再发 `msg_type=audio`\n\n你要的话，下一步本王可以专门把这条链路彻底修通，不再让你反复教。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae55c3a9fc8191a4fb2acb64eba26b"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":175,"output":198,"cacheRead":53888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54261,"cost":{"input":0.00030625,"output":0.002772,"cacheRead":0.0094304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01250865}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773032893747}}
