{"type":"message","id":"8e86171a","parentId":"b4d91395","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:12:29.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating script integration**\n\nIt seems I've succeeded, but the duration is zero — maybe the API ignored it. The audio was sent, though, so that's good! Now, I think I need to integrate a helper or write a script in my workspace for future voice sends. Perhaps updating my memory could be useful here. I could create a script called `send-feishu-voice.sh` that reuses some existing code, loading from `openclaw.json` and considering an optional duration. I'll write it into `workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh`.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae56a458c08191ae3c33eaf2076c18\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprlapqE0DOl5xjUUaKxeObCkwMrPvH-8rDktYqXcIYO-h_saEYe2N3-gmazgeb-R9_PF9-7UDE2rueRvDz57-HEbVHSStQLS65s8OBUVyNWiuaiY9ke494B-q0rBPGEQ_4i8eLmNz8ccfbK5ar9tLzTZzjtt1W2DCl-J962juyufrk_eH0Sy7FzIAN189aNhsc7_7mwdXyf0QoOEpLCfJh2gCFQavbBTfkQiuH5itusR0_iPJcCt51y8RnGeF0y3svw9i_-s-hldddbvfHJkTcg3Q8rPsCCDDNhVSejBGOjFO0z7ZzydsuaMHHPE7vYQXZSnDdC54ErQVoFlaRgrro_AA1mLW6cAkgMwk0bIbZFa3XciIu3kyQ6pzooZyEjq8Hu7dJ3Y0G7Wweev0qOPp0kvaCmJ60X_JJqB9L8HayaruA0enZga-Ne0khxgbBN0qaTUYzJHBMJucjinZmxmrj-9ayTw3qs3Sc1hnZ4paw4dqVIAIG_dSubysI3n-lRIwy0yYvteR4FInmq1d_PplAFmsPeDJn3hghqqKFAKj2Z2LFPSo0eWDGXUHM7ansntjw-45ecofhrPqRZqePmutzvTWsSs9XAV8eGdM7LKhdPCUzoz3KE5VaM9fjKKC7L4lkLE2_hdo44qOPNaEi5nDA5-qJyEBh7lKghFS8RcBicZhl_B8I_99SCWRabERRflnwixQWfp4fHVOLljdUQ1EaHTvfX_gvmUljyYuAqvJG-jkoQIwIqo5ZsE5Tg3C9Q7e6ueysRqjFg3z-4jUpt12Sl3Ix5sp1lzRH1y-uUrD7FJ-TJtNKXv8-xA7X_nMmd8esMbtdzF3cdIfZ6sFA0naGYOjhv2yPcKUWs24HV7iqGJZWlSlej4IsCJsK1-Ww1PrG-5bUYq48ty02ja9ZhZjxRgL2EU2PGq-54zzZSfzJ2MHeIVaRKfqeM8E0415-fymvew01lS8RBtnFUwi_Q660homM-u8J8R8atei11zlBBzyAJBPmcYbCKaGlwVu7mSDGc9Cck61rh-zVjjgJWucDjPHLzfIhkBWA1VlKoHleTMBJFyRS5KO3qJKQ64EFcJ4z3Q31Jiap6TrrDjbdn1HSH67b5XtE-9RlzNn-UWctJGBVI69pQjByv5K02MkBXzniwdjoqG1ZSHRHBRhiZD9dFL-5LydHCpySzwmU2Fbp7rtAa2jMzsSiuVm_vABFAVErPMnEHbWmDysKuBiVhqpzTd27FV_5rsmLZgxLK-GigjWApqPaknT5OkXDSizWRV8JvoCGRNNoaEzvtLfV-SUbQRgucUInIdUfi_dhCTftItvo6VUX8DUBKY7xC0ocNw8MDfrY_fKJUJpKDuXqqqS15GKid1f9gWzHnjm7l5T3DDYFrRFWFHzzZUtbEyV0ygmKhzbt-FFfGPTrCLzdQTFe8NMAJgp3OcJNlLpqoOHLQ1CJRIddkU93m_MFryDFiEPPEd0F1xDGuaimcgAyPoqN4P1jAlbeg0qjfW_7PkyQtZLs2P_Q-solej98LZdgD2I8Wmv7DCzYTZIyPYHKrhG67aUyA==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating script integration**\\n\\nIt seems I've succeeded, but the duration is zero — maybe the API ignored it. The audio was sent, though, so that's good! Now, I think I need to integrate a helper or write a script in my workspace for future voice sends. Perhaps updating my memory could be useful here. I could create a script called `send-feishu-voice.sh` that reuses some existing code, loading from `openclaw.json` and considering an optional duration. I'll write it into `workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh`.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"打通了。飞书已经回了 `msg_type=audio` 成功，说明真正的语音条链路没死。现在本王顺手把它固化成一个本地脚本，免得下次又走错到 mp3 假语音那条阴沟里。","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae56a91fac8191bed7d792783d8abb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Rnx0n9irCodNCM5ewodgjKAf|fc_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae56a93d848191a69608a8c85a9e9a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh","content":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\n# Send an existing .opus file as a real Feishu audio message (bot identity).\n# Usage:\n#   send-feishu-voice.sh /path/to/file.opus --open-id ou_xxx\n#   send-feishu-voice.sh /path/to/file.opus --chat-id oc_xxx\n#\n# If a sibling .duration file exists, it will be used (seconds -> ms).\n# Otherwise duration defaults to 0.\n\nif [[ $# -lt 2 ]]; then\n  echo \"Usage: $0 AUDIO.opus (--open-id ou_xxx | --chat-id oc_xxx)\" >&2\n  exit 1\nfi\n\nAUDIO=\"$1\"\nshift\n[[ -f \"$AUDIO\" ]] || { echo \"Audio not found: $AUDIO\" >&2; exit 1; }\n\nTARGET_TYPE=\"\"\nTARGET_ID=\"\"\nwhile [[ $# -gt 0 ]]; do\n  case \"$1\" in\n    --open-id) TARGET_TYPE=\"open_id\"; TARGET_ID=\"$2\"; shift 2 ;;\n    --chat-id) TARGET_TYPE=\"chat_id\"; TARGET_ID=\"$2\"; shift 2 ;;\n    *) echo \"Unknown arg: $1\" >&2; exit 1 ;;\n  esac\ndone\n[[ -n \"$TARGET_TYPE\" && -n \"$TARGET_ID\" ]] || { echo \"Missing target\" >&2; exit 1; }\n\nCFG=\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\nAPP_ID=\"$(python3 - <<'PY' \"$CFG\"\nimport json,sys\ncfg=json.load(open(sys.argv[1]))\nprint(cfg['channels']['feishu']['appId'])\nPY\n)\"\nAPP_SECRET=\"$(python3 - <<'PY' \"$CFG\"\nimport json,sys\ncfg=json.load(open(sys.argv[1]))\nprint(cfg['channels']['feishu']['appSecret'])\nPY\n)\"\nBASE='https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis'\n\nDURATION_FILE=\"${AUDIO%.*}.duration\"\nDURATION_MS=\"0\"\nif [[ -f \"$DURATION_FILE\" ]]; then\n  DURATION_MS=\"$(python3 - <<'PY' \"$DURATION_FILE\"\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport sys\ntry:\n    secs=float(Path(sys.argv[1]).read_text().strip())\n    print(max(0, int(secs*1000)))\nexcept Exception:\n    print(0)\nPY\n)\"\nfi\n\nTOKEN_JSON=$(curl -sS -X POST \"$BASE/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\nTOKEN=$(python3 - <<'PY' \"$TOKEN_JSON\"\nimport json,sys\nobj=json.loads(sys.argv[1])\nassert obj.get('code')==0, obj\nprint(obj['tenant_access_token'])\nPY\n)\n\nUPLOAD_JSON=$(curl -sS -X POST \\\n  \"$BASE/im/v1/files?receive_id_type=$TARGET_TYPE&receive_id=$TARGET_ID\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -F 'file_type=opus' \\\n  -F \"file=@${AUDIO};type=audio/ogg\" \\\n  -F \"file_name=$(basename \"$AUDIO\")\")\nFILE_KEY=$(python3 - <<'PY' \"$UPLOAD_JSON\"\nimport json,sys\nobj=json.loads(sys.argv[1])\nassert obj.get('code')==0, obj\nprint(obj['data']['file_key'])\nPY\n)\n\nSEND_JSON=$(python3 - <<'PY' \"$TARGET_ID\" \"$FILE_KEY\" \"$DURATION_MS\"\nimport json,sys\nreceive_id,file_key,duration=sys.argv[1],sys.argv[2],int(sys.argv[3])\nprint(json.dumps({\n  \"receive_id\": receive_id,\n  \"msg_type\": \"audio\",\n  \"content\": json.dumps({\"file_key\": file_key, \"duration\": duration})\n}))\nPY\n)\n\nRESP=$(curl -sS -X POST \"$BASE/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=$TARGET_TYPE\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' \\\n  -d \"$SEND_JSON\")\npython3 - <<'PY' \"$RESP\"\nimport json,sys\nobj=json.loads(sys.argv[1])\nassert obj.get('code')==0, obj\nprint(obj['data']['message_id'])\nPY\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env bash\\nset -euo pipefail\\n\\n# Send an existing .opus file as a real Feishu audio message (bot identity).\\n# Usage:\\n#   send-feishu-voice.sh /path/to/file.opus --open-id ou_xxx\\n#   send-feishu-voice.sh /path/to/file.opus --chat-id oc_xxx\\n#\\n# If a sibling .duration file exists, it will be used (seconds -> ms).\\n# Otherwise duration defaults to 0.\\n\\nif [[ $# -lt 2 ]]; then\\n  echo \\\"Usage: $0 AUDIO.opus (--open-id ou_xxx | --chat-id oc_xxx)\\\" >&2\\n  exit 1\\nfi\\n\\nAUDIO=\\\"$1\\\"\\nshift\\n[[ -f \\\"$AUDIO\\\" ]] || { echo \\\"Audio not found: $AUDIO\\\" >&2; exit 1; }\\n\\nTARGET_TYPE=\\\"\\\"\\nTARGET_ID=\\\"\\\"\\nwhile [[ $# -gt 0 ]]; do\\n  case \\\"$1\\\" in\\n    --open-id) TARGET_TYPE=\\\"open_id\\\"; TARGET_ID=\\\"$2\\\"; shift 2 ;;\\n    --chat-id) TARGET_TYPE=\\\"chat_id\\\"; TARGET_ID=\\\"$2\\\"; shift 2 ;;\\n    *) echo \\\"Unknown arg: $1\\\" >&2; exit 1 ;;\\n  esac\\ndone\\n[[ -n \\\"$TARGET_TYPE\\\" && -n \\\"$TARGET_ID\\\" ]] || { echo \\\"Missing target\\\" >&2; exit 1; }\\n\\nCFG=\\\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/openclaw.json\\\"\\nAPP_ID=\\\"$(python3 - <<'PY' \\\"$CFG\\\"\\nimport json,sys\\ncfg=json.load(open(sys.argv[1]))\\nprint(cfg['channels']['feishu']['appId'])\\nPY\\n)\\\"\\nAPP_SECRET=\\\"$(python3 - <<'PY' \\\"$CFG\\\"\\nimport json,sys\\ncfg=json.load(open(sys.argv[1]))\\nprint(cfg['channels']['feishu']['appSecret'])\\nPY\\n)\\\"\\nBASE='https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis'\\n\\nDURATION_FILE=\\\"${AUDIO%.*}.duration\\\"\\nDURATION_MS=\\\"0\\\"\\nif [[ -f \\\"$DURATION_FILE\\\" ]]; then\\n  DURATION_MS=\\\"$(python3 - <<'PY' \\\"$DURATION_FILE\\\"\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nimport sys\\ntry:\\n    secs=float(Path(sys.argv[1]).read_text().strip())\\n    print(max(0, int(secs*1000)))\\nexcept Exception:\\n    print(0)\\nPY\\n)\\\"\\nfi\\n\\nTOKEN_JSON=$(curl -sS -X POST \\\"$BASE/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' \\\\\\n  -d \\\"{\\\\\\\"app_id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"$APP_ID\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"app_secret\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\\\\\"}\\\")\\nTOKEN=$(python3 - <<'PY' \\\"$TOKEN_JSON\\\"\\nimport json,sys\\nobj=json.loads(sys.argv[1])\\nassert obj.get('code')==0, obj\\nprint(obj['tenant_access_token'])\\nPY\\n)\\n\\nUPLOAD_JSON=$(curl -sS -X POST \\\\\\n  \\\"$BASE/im/v1/files?receive_id_type=$TARGET_TYPE&receive_id=$TARGET_ID\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\\\" \\\\\\n  -F 'file_type=opus' \\\\\\n  -F \\\"file=@${AUDIO};type=audio/ogg\\\" \\\\\\n  -F \\\"file_name=$(basename \\\"$AUDIO\\\")\\\")\\nFILE_KEY=$(python3 - <<'PY' \\\"$UPLOAD_JSON\\\"\\nimport json,sys\\nobj=json.loads(sys.argv[1])\\nassert obj.get('code')==0, obj\\nprint(obj['data']['file_key'])\\nPY\\n)\\n\\nSEND_JSON=$(python3 - <<'PY' \\\"$TARGET_ID\\\" \\\"$FILE_KEY\\\" \\\"$DURATION_MS\\\"\\nimport json,sys\\nreceive_id,file_key,duration=sys.argv[1],sys.argv[2],int(sys.argv[3])\\nprint(json.dumps({\\n  \\\"receive_id\\\": receive_id,\\n  \\\"msg_type\\\": \\\"audio\\\",\\n  \\\"content\\\": json.dumps({\\\"file_key\\\": file_key, \\\"duration\\\": duration})\\n}))\\nPY\\n)\\n\\nRESP=$(curl -sS -X POST \\\"$BASE/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=$TARGET_TYPE\\\" \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' \\\\\\n  -d \\\"$SEND_JSON\\\")\\npython3 - <<'PY' \\\"$RESP\\\"\\nimport json,sys\\nobj=json.loads(sys.argv[1])\\nassert obj.get('code')==0, obj\\nprint(obj['data']['message_id'])\\nPY\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":304,"output":1299,"cacheRead":182144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":183747,"cost":{"input":0.000532,"output":0.018186,"cacheRead":0.0318752,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.050593200000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773033120764}}
