{"type":"message","id":"e69d36cc","parentId":"23194555","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:13:05.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 修好了，苏神。\n\n结果直接给你：\n- **飞书真实语音条已经发成功了**\n- 本王刚刚用机器人身份把现成的 `.opus` 语音**真的发到你飞书里了**\n- 飞书返回成功消息 ID：\n  `om_x100b55d1220be0a4b4b3697b8f52fcb`\n\n这次本王确认了真正的问题：\n- **错的链路**：`tts/mp3 -> asVoice`\n- **对的链路**：`.opus -> 上传 file_type=opus -> 发送 msg_type=audio`\n\n我还顺手给你落了一个本地脚本，免得以后再踩坑：\n- `scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh`\n\n用法：\n- 发给你本人：\n  `scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh /path/to/file.opus --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f`\n- 发到群：\n  `scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh /path/to/file.opus --chat-id oc_xxx`\n\n另外，本王也把这条经验写进记忆了：\n- 飞书语音必须走 **opus** 正道\n- 不能再拿 mp3 假装语音\n\n要不要下一步本王继续把它再往前补一层：\n**把“文本 -> 生成 opus -> 自动发飞书语音”做成一条龙**？\n这样你以后一句话，本王直接吐语音，不用再手动喂文件。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae56db0c3081918ee870aefb07ae1c"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":194,"output":354,"cacheRead":184320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":184868,"cost":{"input":0.0003395,"output":0.004956,"cacheRead":0.032256,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0375515}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773033176849}}
