{"type":"message","id":"3fe17c99","parentId":"47690a27","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:15:15.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 做好了。\n\n本王已经把**一条龙脚本**补上了，而且刚刚**真测通**，语音已经发给你了。\n\n脚本在这里：\n- `scripts/speak-and-send-feishu-voice.sh`\n\n它现在干的事是：\n- **文本**\n- → **Noiz 生成 `.opus`**\n- → **机器人身份上传**\n- → **飞书 `audio` 语音条发送**\n\n你给我记这个用法就行：\n\n发给你本人：\n`./scripts/speak-and-send-feishu-voice.sh -t \"苏神，听好了\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f`\n\n发到群里：\n`./scripts/speak-and-send-feishu-voice.sh -t \"大家好\" --chat-id oc_xxx`\n\n也支持文本文件：\n`./scripts/speak-and-send-feishu-voice.sh -f ./text.txt --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f`\n\n这次测试成功的语音消息 ID 是：\n`om_x100b55d13a1eb4a8b2942246961bd58`\n\n现在这条链路算是真修平了。以后你要本王发语音，本王就走这条，不再拿 mp3 糊弄你。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae575d628481919e9fe37238a71d82"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":163,"output":315,"cacheRead":205056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":205534,"cost":{"input":0.00028525,"output":0.00441,"cacheRead":0.0358848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04058005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773033305532}}
