{"type":"message","id":"fe055c03","parentId":"ebebd157","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:22:47.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying heartbeat logging**\n\nI need to address the heartbeat logging configuration, which should have entries every 30 minutes. However, it seems the recent logs are based on manual tests rather than actual heartbeat data. It’s essential to clarify this distinction so we get accurate real-time readings. I wonder if there’s a way to fix this discrepancy in the logs before moving forward with any analysis or conclusions. Let’s ensure the next entries reflect the actual heartbeat correctly.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae592343e08191b8eb5cafec0993b3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprlkmbfTogoN_6N0PLqR6SchAWjrbYHOd75djeX0hUdDZ0jGinBiLofiZnX1LgOlvuYZIluITpYvqaIKUbZAkC_T5vty772AmYHf8TDNdkb71hQ3z2_K5nd3ZrDdmV1U5oshfPtCmMGzYqKHNS_MOwHP1e2WHbQPsA8tnCBmYTP2EQGuclEOjF8oGCEnrO25clvbOAAK3PApRt9leF_Zeyn54IT9C1JwU5PeaoIHv7Kk7YVUXOXI7n8_vs7gs2pv4LsUzHBh71igMQtISFkTvQPKslSvo6GtuqqCr3peGoWVQzvMIjgtxFaOh6oNxZ-b9Tp1mhYmJ6OB_MPSHKFPH4Egop24mCnKAReQqTeo869pqLMnuMFi8dI_gBWKIZcD2Lr8ZNfFnadtv95aco0EY_TbXDHDCiPSb5_QixD4q3jqrIkRsMBZxbPRnzRhrGzQfHejJYx6fsexHlDcz_bQf-hEa4qGoLXQcRvJbvV_JS9dCmVTi0QbCDtP9NgrjRmtopJR-0pRruK_mcDKArXvno_uUJY50Bqptma0-QvBmvLzvRUDyL0kHcpT_TgQiSv91sHbLhDYbcEUXpQZS9JsNR40o1ivIpt5TuzDbJuTTG6OTbazKCTUgdsl8iOsEZU9cLHFaOnG6a0pqnoC7shIHMOOZQw-pyGj5MtEPhUR82mU1XVFT_KOBhEgUmmOsam8cbEPq8SlMiS_0aKsGBLtRhAQ3AUE0V6RoyanSbdRmhSnv6NOM2zxTqwGDtBgoofuZsAyz3pKDZMmZMq3WqG-P9hSeDFNmRJnwgrcRlo4DLvaSvC5U35QhE6p8yJp74K9VxatpT7YEyzVsJKsRpqtJoui-TRtRIlCZyNEYcGeG9pEkhp-nJ8p2xK8JJPMGkgwQdght38-rrfucnUFXuX8kpxpiBJC6XKPdQx4-aRG0BQlorMVXzVA_yYSD7yY7UXO8xZp9\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying heartbeat logging**\\n\\nI need to address the heartbeat logging configuration, which should have entries every 30 minutes. However, it seems the recent logs are based on manual tests rather than actual heartbeat data. It’s essential to clarify this distinction so we get accurate real-time readings. I wonder if there’s a way to fix this discrepancy in the logs before moving forward with any analysis or conclusions. Let’s ensure the next entries reflect the actual heartbeat correctly.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 心跳周期是 **30 分钟一次**。\n\n本来配置里就是：\n- **every: 30m**\n- 生效时段：**07:00 - 00:00**\n\n你今天觉得本王几分钟发了三遍，不是心跳抽风，是因为那几条里有的是：\n- **你让我测试心跳**\n- **你让我跑一次真的心跳**\n- **你又让我测试语音**\n- **我在修飞书语音链路时又主动发了几条验证**\n\n也就是说，**那不是 30 分钟内自动心跳连发三次**，而是我们今天在拿你当靶场疯狂联调。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae5926c5548191844f97ddb85e9fc2"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":736,"output":187,"cacheRead":207488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":208411,"cost":{"input":0.001288,"output":0.002618,"cacheRead":0.0363104,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0402164}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773033759319}}
