penclaw.json` 的基线校验还在报 `FAILED`\n   - 这事还没彻底修平，本王记着呢\n\n你要是愿意，本王还能下一条给你分成：\n- **长期记忆**\n- **今天临时测试结论**\n- **待修问题**\n三类列给你。","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae5a6d8b1481918de98dd08a2a1a6f"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":508,"output":502,"cacheRead":213120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":214130,"cost":{"input":0.000889,"output":0.0070279999999999995,"cacheRead":0.037295999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.045212999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773034089379}}
