现在使用\n\n本王也已经把这次清理写进今天的记忆了。\n\n如果你愿意，本王下一步可以继续顺手做：\n- **把旧 Feishu 备份目录也彻底审一遍**\n- 或者\n- **把 openclaw.json 再做一次“非路径类脏配置”精修**\n\n今天这波，算是把配置层面的海底淤泥铲得差不多了。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae5d86d6d48191ad055591bd0ee553"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":408,"output":461,"cacheRead":224128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":224997,"cost":{"input":0.000714,"output":0.006454,"cacheRead":0.0392224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0463904}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773034883199}}
