{"type":"message","id":"eecb7d9d","parentId":"dc694106","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:54:52.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying missing context**\n\nI need to ask what needs fixing, but it seems I'm missing some context because previous messages were queued and omitted. It’s important for me to get clear information to help effectively. I'll make sure to ask a concise question to gather the necessary details. That way, I can avoid any misunderstandings and provide the best assistance possible!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7cc9274481918f180d42dfb80a6b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprnzLpbFqmONIecRgj8NZAto2J1EC05MV8P8mrZshcjBPbMAilZ9122QEv1Q-vPnM7MnQmSM6TE-H8YS70Tm81jhDihUbQVVlplluOHfAwNKp5Zix9_6HJ8yRy8LBOGiUFuqwXA3p5WyTKKds1B8s8QlKPzA607gknqn6GoGsrzJStvyuTIoJy8BuXiIfGu0reHemMBhnJxlUo6ShSiLWb25s3kQKwjYRS5e0xKXDCNtNozuGLjg6TAgOcyGo5CrG4Zz5s4RPzQvs5rvulQ1x93X9226oHBGxi61VgJzZYvmQoa9Vc7ZqyHtuBftMMbY4i-wWNZjYrSil86HXWgshv2pYrQsaQ2oK0KuL8NbFvZc8mQOi9-2PMlpaatTsbWE6sAWZhldP7X4UDud14GGxwa7EiFNCrO79q6q5AVA9In_mUHqxoWaJc1iNMyNJa_BXDhenBrmIfCRQmv3PIk5psvGR17868XZ5h6g0XnjQhfHg-Wd0Xd_ya7vfZg1QJRSjMoe4so919AnfOHGE9lXhb-ZOFLcpK7G4UqOBEHA_TnbKa1GV3j-zvREvRsyO6Bh2ojDcfp1AB9bKN1xqbHbe2CO2SQUGs_J8RxqTxu7M6xxS8Jz4OZeUl6leSeb7unP9gyNwq1Xi3886ciLzdvjKVt9s_o8xHA_rw0mncA2zMLsENQS_yev_3eqhCiMO0irj-xjIVE8v68ohJJqMM48_jhR3hlhTdIMqSzXk-QA4DtwHSQhSVTg2KR8ogZNyQMKGZxYzZjwc6CFLefBmezO_-f_BM04tjVi7CVk-N0aXG-4jy6v7FLihGIHfybtQ6gCFdLhDdQCHTnDVeQWk-9Q7hSzG4ghFxYtE8aG36QuUlZ5lWaihqqipnEmaqEUgDsJyW37xiRBn2UHc6LQ3tpk916j3DcDPmRv5KOb1InazuarO3ngDgE2aqL4wEVsd7UCVGoUh\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying missing context**\\n\\nI need to ask what needs fixing, but it seems I'm missing some context because previous messages were queued and omitted. It’s important for me to get clear information to help effectively. I'll make sure to ask a concise question to gather the necessary details. That way, I can avoid any misunderstandings and provide the best assistance possible!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 修什么，你倒是说清楚啊苏神。\n\n你刚才连着发了几条，但我这边现在只看到最后这句“你修复一下”，**没看到具体对象**。\n\n直接回我这三样里至少一个：\n- **哪个东西坏了**  \n- **报错/现象是什么**  \n- **你希望修到什么状态**\n\n你一说清，本王就开钳。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7ccb1ac48191bf19432884c7e3fb"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":593,"output":129,"cacheRead":219776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":220498,"cost":{"input":0.00103775,"output":0.0018059999999999999,"cacheRead":0.038460799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.041304549999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773042883770}}
