{"type":"message","id":"5a0c40d7","parentId":"18fe95d7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:58:33.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Troubleshooting plugin issues**\n\nI need to figure out how to use the feishu-troubleshoot skill because there seems to be a plugin issue. I should start by reviewing the skill's documentation to understand how it works. Making sure I'm familiar with it might help me diagnose or fix the problem more effectively. Okay, let's see what I can learn from the skill details to solve this plugin issue properly!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7da667188191980c62d0513f3c68\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprn2ojTtaMf5_kWu7SoXLZg95JznArOuafUqk5Tg6ohRD5zCqGNb3f8ikvGJobA5tgMIacO-pSfwvyn5QF6hsl7Z2QN9Tt24kh8ba08wlXAqF3yiEmdKssRhZLpGV1iHqt4r0OCHgAtp1mZgp9gRhUZ090OcR1zw4YpXVBA7Mur5oiyWsweNaypWlHVtaY2HhIvB6R7EatnA4ze4zYEDkZYLbeQJBc-4IBns_nI86tQii_nkT-Vk22ScHIzncclsoXGLSrnrcoo0i16G3auwHgNr-0eAm6FSvjKy3ghIVAUPBtGfw4mtcwOYJV1bsXCmiHv6j4BO22Mfo0G8TE_fH53tQqMePf084yyS_XLzgALiygvHzz0DawIoWIFNA-HFgTWfrXphWtv448_iLV9bIOnE-BeHlQNl1HjN-WLB-g4tO6fvwDRDMxV9C5b-R389sXNZtQUSCtJu_qrsqcln3Sovy9HCIQopGGNvqtPYUpfh4XmS10TbsxjcZbAwk-Qh52ISodrbGYyNRpRHTj--nDm4WdhNHXru0TKNHPP8F_v5ZBz5qjMwab9vzoTh1q6beHxZ0fXCamENKWsh9iP3q4a9IJGsRnoFCw-YJ87HHBFQSfmglbBmXo0sFlbEHyus14JDwK57Lt88rYmZgPisoyEoyg4tb7h50p3r_CAj_MlwheD9DFid6sl_9k57GOOhNStrNAJnwUZNCajjVIn3HZwVe8fUj7Jd0W2agEx-PVYIU5YvuXdIKXsicvdPAEYK5xL2hYcon8ZPKYgZ0TJKxrfc6l6EQWkcqcZLn6cNRud4wECzRtFe5QZxnzUVt8cVgXxnk5BRHj8Wb8jPS9KMKoHJfdHDI9Q4ZMhxLYIqAQQ9IeBrc-0kpXiUsgsw38-UsSslSaSF8BGo5xma10WeST1vPNOhOam3QXTwAbWHPmhUdUy8=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Troubleshooting plugin issues**\\n\\nI need to figure out how to use the feishu-troubleshoot skill because there seems to be a plugin issue. I should start by reviewing the skill's documentation to understand how it works. Making sure I'm familiar with it might help me diagnose or fix the problem more effectively. Okay, let's see what I can learn from the skill details to solve this plugin issue properly!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Agdo1NiUJhGfW8J80MJGURC5|fc_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7da89f188191ada88a7f8b959b95","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":826,"output":68,"cacheRead":220288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":221182,"cost":{"input":0.0014455,"output":0.0009519999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0385504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.040947899999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773043104299}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a8225df","parentId":"5a0c40d7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:58:33.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Agdo1NiUJhGfW8J80MJGURC5|fc_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7da89f188191ada88a7f8b959b95","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-troubleshoot\ndescription: |\n  飞书插件问题排查工具。包含常见问题 FAQ 和深度诊断命令（/feishu_doctor）。\n\n  常见问题可随时查阅。诊断命令用于排查复杂问题（多次授权仍失败、自动授权无法解决等），\n  会检查账户配置、API 连通性、应用权限、用户授权状态，并生成详细的诊断报告和解决方案。\n\n---\n\n# 飞书插件问题排查\n\n## ❓ 常见问题（FAQ）\n\n### 卡片按钮点击无反应\n\n**现象**：点击卡片按钮后没有任何反应，然后提示报错.\n\n**原因**：应用未开通「消息卡片回传交互」权限。\n\n**解决步骤**：\n\n1. 登录飞书开放平台：https://open.feishu.cn/app\n2. 选择您的应用 → **事件与回调**\n3. 在回调配置中,修改订阅方式为\"长链接\"并添加回调 \"卡片回传交互\"(card.action.trigger)\n4. 创建应用版本 → 提交审核 → 发布\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 诊断命令（深度工具）\n\n**注意**：诊断命令仅用于排查复杂/疑难的**权限相关问题**。常规权限问题会自动触发授权流程，无需手动诊断。\n\n**何时使用诊断**：\n- 多次授权后仍然报错\n- 自动授权流程无法解决的问题\n- 需要查看完整的权限配置状态\n\n**使用方法**：\n\n在飞书聊天会话中直接输入（作为用户消息发送）：\n\n/feishu doctor\n\n诊断命令会检查：\n\n- **📋 诊断摘要**（首先展示）：\n  - 总体状态（✅ 正常 / ⚠️ 警告 / ❌ 失败）\n  - 发现的问题列表和简要描述\n\n- **环境信息**：\n  - 插件版本\n\n- **账号信息**：\n  - 凭证完整性（appId, appSecret 掩码）\n  - 账户启用状态\n  - API 连通性测试\n  - Bot 信息（名称和 openId）\n\n- **应用身份权限**：\n  - 应用已开通的必需权限数量\n  - 缺失的必需权限列表\n  - 一键申请链接（自动带上缺失权限参数）\n\n- **用户身份权限**：\n  - 用户授权状态统计（✓ 有效 / ⟳ 需刷新 / ✗ 已过期）\n  - Token 自动刷新状态（是否包含 offline_access）\n  - 权限对照表（应用已开通 vs 用户已授权，逐项对比）\n  - 应用权限缺失时的申请指引和链接\n  - 用户授权不足时的重新授权操作方法\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773043113297}}
{"type":"message","id":"a56fc5ee","parentId":"8a8225df","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:58:45.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering token management**\n\nI need to think about handling token expiration effectively. The best approach here seems to be revoking the existing token to refresh it when it expires. Since it mentions needing a refresh, I could suggest reauthorization too. It’s worth noting that if the user is facing expiration issues, using feishu_oauth to revoke might help. But ultimately, the user is asking how to handle it, not specifically for me to do it. I should mention trying revoking and auto reauthorization as part of the solution.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7dab6fc08191a1039f717ec0b147\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprn2uYciOvhb2Zv_4aSc0p_J9OqjWtUHCU_drKOygUGtwzxzGmwx6HDVsRlzBf9tKDZUSj0V1snhDLNH761tO68LtGqsWN6iEyaon0BIDZd2Kec5WokbDbp_LvN8CwlJU8ewEk236UMawYj0m5hDQSaUAXEOK42yX9YtU5Ap6WYUs5bkpp3AfOBspj607c8pVYXpimLSxgNkmsTNfWz29kM0iJ55sa87sfSYIiemCH7vaLKYNm20TziBAEQSxVcp7G_ESD16BWNOF-GErosSt8nVCbcjpE59V8RWfrlAIsjuHVxNqQEpFUD7T88ZFnBLNM01T0-8VD0I7FF3E7yt6ZMIsdvMcjzyUgeTSeaPkdOKvyVXD6Z2FAMSfOq9YCR4BdCh4o7x2NJ_YMxp1qQ-NsZeLh1si6-rDhkFeVBn8bN7CMqkSaI4KCOY0SmUPrOO9k1IDGlWkYTHBFleDbpB-zQA9mpvUj6htjKuHNl63OZBjR_DunjEItmu0cQ_BplejX3GJoHNo6AA0fPlIsbdG9khpGzqQN34wxtI9ECKTWX8Ke7E0ZXjtol3_txEyOdcAlyqHBsOiGr2a3wDFRUpAyq3ZBKsXJ7Ux_t3G2lGB_IdvZm_2V99MxutCPDwhrzD2Tet_24TPH07pe98fU6dfinpSYQwxTgZPrtb1uRuc_sl5ilqwjQgx4eEz7hhAUbp-Jg_Nx_6qxC1ygXIPWSZpLWUDmKtT2TFSwQU02_UhCWA1Zl5uA3hIpyJmsfC7r_rI3gcSEBm0WIJnRkHe2JtCmukfh0_BNPZqCxC9ksksRlxznKzitXGK4pZ--Us90w1gJFdZyloinOKXZ7gn80kA4nNdjXLrewNXexV9hc0tmtciN5PpgrsJkRG46Uk7ZQcXcdGRXKLUBHf5WCF6zzEG3gjBovOqOC_PcG3MNQrXWan9gVSkQZQH5HCqjyvWVE1oTSma3wY6toCqc7Ozx_hT-ti8wnOKP7LGW01Fx9wBq6lyi8eUa9UxfMa_dt0P7MZq9lOu61n_5uXyrtxuyYJl_mfHE8iPabYXi-Ny4d6DnCMbmaG2FI4pHFUitrK9dm5DSfSjD0iDDG2CirEWGbAVcNtKD3UC_hEs1Xp5XM9nd2D14gAHLdXJ32zBDLTwrya_2t11e5a9OpnRaaaw1kd8S_aFSxzEq2Rrj8VjQOX8FK-qfpE=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering token management**\\n\\nI need to think about handling token expiration effectively. The best approach here seems to be revoking the existing token to refresh it when it expires. Since it mentions needing a refresh, I could suggest reauthorization too. It’s worth noting that if the user is facing expiration issues, using feishu_oauth to revoke might help. But ultimately, the user is asking how to handle it, not specifically for me to do it. I should mention trying revoking and auto reauthorization as part of the solution.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这个提示的意思很直接：\n\n- **应用身份权限本身大概率没大问题**\n- 但**用户身份授权 token 需要刷新**\n- 现在状态是：\n  **1 个用户里，0 个有效，1 个需刷新**\n\n一般这么处理：\n\n### 先做最省事的处理\n直接**重新走一次用户授权**。\n\n如果插件支持自动刷新，而且用户授权里带了 `offline_access`，理论上它应该能自己续；  \n但既然已经提示 **“用户身份权限检查未通过 / 需刷新”**，说明这次自动续没成功，最稳的就是**重新授权一次**。\n\n### 对你现在这个场景，推荐顺序\n1. **先撤销当前用户授权**\n2. **再重新授权**\n\n在 OpenClaw 这边，处理思路就是：\n- 调用 **`feishu_oauth` 的 revoke**\n- 撤销后，系统会自动重新发起授权流程\n\n也就是一句话：\n**先清旧 token，再重新授权。**\n\n### 为什么不是“等一等”\n因为这不是“已过期”，而是“需刷新但没刷新成功”。\n这种状态最烦，继续拖通常只会反复报：\n- 用户身份权限检查未通过\n- token 需刷新\n- 某些用户身份工具调用失败\n\n### 如果你要自己判断是否更深层有问题\n那就跑一次：\n**`/feishu doctor`**\n\n它会把这几个关键点都告诉你：\n- 应用权限是否缺失\n- 用户授权是否缺 scope\n- 是否带 `offline_access`\n- 自动刷新链路为什么没成功\n\n### 本王给你的建议\n你现在先别绕：\n**直接撤销并重新授权一次**，这是最快的解法。\n\n如果你要，本王下一步可以直接帮你做：\n1. 撤销当前授权\n2. 等系统重新拉起授权\n3. 你授权完，本王再帮你验证是否恢复正常\n\n你回我一句：\n**“直接处理”**  \n本王就开搞。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7daedc94819189f9d61f9819222c"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":749,"output":529,"cacheRead":221056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":222334,"cost":{"input":0.00131075,"output":0.007406,"cacheRead":0.0386848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04740155}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773043113308}}
