. 还在记着的待关注点\n- Git 子模块和一些新目录改动还没系统整理完\n- 飞书语音链路虽然通了，但**音色还没完全调到最满意**\n\n你要的话，本王下一条可以直接给你分成：\n- **长期记忆**\n- **今天新增**\n- **待办/未完成**\n三栏清单。","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7ea56ea0819186c2d87175fa53bd"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":751,"output":556,"cacheRead":222464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":223771,"cost":{"input":0.0013142499999999999,"output":0.007784,"cacheRead":0.0389312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04802945}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773043356782}}
