{"type":"message","id":"a3047761","parentId":"9c02e30a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T08:04:53.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Organizing information concisely**\n\nI'm considering how to present an answer in a concise manner, possibly in a list format. Grouping related items could make the information clearer and easier to digest. I want to ensure that the user gets the key points without unnecessary details, so I'll focus on the most relevant aspects. By keeping everything well-organized, I'm aiming to enhance readability and comprehension for the user. Let's see how this goes!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7f18d08481919d3fd10cbd3031b1\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprn8acTFT_PbqDdkCaBc5msdkJe7gFjxMBCr0RSouHa1nNUqTA4ML-kA5o_2Z2TRTNwE5IUtHljmtHvLAjQCDtNW6rcGMSM1IslCu1_FP2C08mb-s7Aw-078ye3nkmLP_Y88cg6bfC_z4b8KVZ983CR7qq0Emy9-Id7Fj8ip6aTj54JYCQMqjCQOmjTl7TKgGpht03gPqFEzQUGFWIkAS-vWi18rM1QM1m4Kp7Ef5WFP26x1iVL0SVE-01hKm8h4acfR4fMhmpyxNQ8kgr6Q0wxsWEg_owRt2sZMzf3SyCC6HoIj1vGO7ugGlXiXh7OQ5LsNkhwIbDQZo4P2lAlbu5dGt-ayqHCbx8v-GPDocwzcWPCcWgp-IVplgev2Dili5dsPobLnvUOEeS94K-HyBnPby-2yzq6u6_qfqH__vTbh2UdjPPfkskk9kwIDp8nNuTKl7R2IONi3X6RwjrbWKk7xNl-wSlXPsTJN5rAGYjTpXVLtjLFhfNp8MJJS03LieT74QkHVRlJWgqpmSJmbuP5gN_Wqjr6AAMaJCkDsGBnSq2RLiU6W6bbTWdENI_gqAEcu7U_BnMLsQ5dyrApEuj0VYC9yvO0bn8Bt_LrhOxnuUbM_N8moFbgz03s9cEDcA3ypyb1qKJmdB1uco1jX4EiHJdAJAV15kus4tefQFw8u8dWaNvnpbVyi--eknPhv2pycPS41sEEYVvzSe7R7q_AHQfXLcw5KKSUddunS1afEVUveg36FpMxUkoSgG3RV_euMmyzlG4gPHkbHqWFA-wClEcUGT2-BM_Bh9SzmnqZPgCepauZS6H7iFaGe4blVI_GJU7f7CyQsEd1cXlAuQDsFYGOYZoqW7VDn4FyQYt8BbcrJ6bb6PGoYi7YNdE17P2mq3\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Organizing information concisely**\\n\\nI'm considering how to present an answer in a concise manner, possibly in a list format. Grouping related items could make the information clearer and easier to digest. I want to ensure that the user gets the key points without unnecessary details, so I'll focus on the most relevant aspects. By keeping everything well-organized, I'm aiming to enhance readability and comprehension for the user. Let's see how this goes!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 现在本王手里能用的技能，主要有这些：\n\n### 飞书系\n- **feishu-channel-rules**：飞书输出规则\n- **feishu-bitable**：多维表格\n- **feishu-calendar**：日历、日程、忙闲\n- **feishu-create-doc**：创建飞书文档\n- **feishu-fetch-doc**：读取飞书文档\n- **feishu-update-doc**：更新飞书文档\n- **feishu-im-read**：读取飞书消息、搜索消息、下载资源\n- **feishu-task**：飞书任务/清单\n- **feishu-troubleshoot**：飞书问题排查\n\n### 网页 / 搜索 / 信息获取\n- **agent-reach**：上网搜、读链接、平台内容获取\n- **multi-search-engine**：多搜索引擎检索\n- **tavily-search / tavily**：AI 搜索\n- **summarize**：总结 URL / 文件\n- **weather**：天气\n\n### OpenClaw / 技能生态 / 系统能力\n- **find-skills**：找技能\n- **skill-vetter**：技能安全审计\n- **clawhub**：安装/更新/发布技能\n- **skill-creator**：创建或更新技能\n- **healthcheck**：主机安全检查\n- **coding-agent**：委托编码代理\n- **mcporter**：MCP 服务调用\n- **1password**：1Password CLI\n- **apple-reminders**：苹果提醒事项\n\n### 内容生成 / 图像 / 设计\n- **baoyu-image-gen**：AI 生图\n- **baoyu-cover-image**：文章封面图\n- **baoyu-article-illustrator**：文章配图\n- **baoyu-infographic**：信息图\n- **baoyu-slide-deck**：幻灯片图\n- **baoyu-comic**：知识漫画\n- **baoyu-xhs-images**：小红书图文图组\n- **baoyu-compress-image**：图片压缩\n- **baoyu-format-markdown**：Markdown 美化\n- **baoyu-markdown-to-html**：Markdown 转 HTML\n- **baoyu-translate**：翻译\n- **baoyu-url-to-markdown**：网页转 Markdown\n\n### 社交平台 / 发布\n- **baoyu-post-to-wechat**：发公众号\n- **baoyu-post-to-weibo**：发微博\n- **baoyu-post-to-x**：发 X\n- **xiaohongshu**：小红书搜索/分析/评论\n\n### 其他\n- **youmind**：Youmind board 操作\n- **gifgrep**：GIF 搜索下载\n\n如果你要，本王下一条可以直接给你整理成：\n1. **我最常用的**\n2. **你目前最值得重点用的**\n3. **今天就能马上派上用场的**","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7f1afe848191bc6d80860bd06402"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":768,"output":672,"cacheRead":224000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":225440,"cost":{"input":0.001344,"output":0.009408,"cacheRead":0.0392,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.049951999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773043471660}}
