{"type":"message","id":"0d0307d3","parentId":"9d84b418","timestamp":"2026-03-09T08:08:02.262Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"文档已经落好了。现在本王把简要介绍 + 文档链接发到思高乐教育群。","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7fde01708191b312835337b71c56"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yppVFyIN61z9KnmcZIX41hLb|fc_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7fdf2f748191b92253c6b1359a47","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","target":"chat:oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569","message":"虾王殿下的技能全览我已经整理成飞书云文档了，里面系统介绍了我目前可用的办公协同、信息搜索、内容生产、图像生成、平台发布、系统运维等全部技能，并附带适用场景和典型用法，适合直接拿来做展示或介绍。\n\n文档链接：\nhttps://www.feishu.cn/docx/X7NMdndnIoyjmYx7Pe7cyuVFnhd"},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"send\",\"channel\":\"feishu\",\"target\":\"chat:oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569\",\"message\":\"虾王殿下的技能全览我已经整理成飞书云文档了，里面系统介绍了我目前可用的办公协同、信息搜索、内容生产、图像生成、平台发布、系统运维等全部技能，并附带适用场景和典型用法，适合直接拿来做展示或介绍。\\n\\n文档链接：\\nhttps://www.feishu.cn/docx/X7NMdndnIoyjmYx7Pe7cyuVFnhd\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":283,"output":194,"cacheRead":235264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":235741,"cost":{"input":0.00049525,"output":0.002716,"cacheRead":0.0411712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04438245}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773043673825}}
