{"type":"message","id":"bfb7f3e3","parentId":"24e72353","timestamp":"2026-03-09T08:08:10.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 搞定了，苏神。\n\n我已经做完这三件事：\n\n1. **整理了一份完整技能说明**\n2. **写成飞书云文档**\n3. **发到思高乐教育群，并配了简要介绍**\n\n### 文档标题\n**虾王殿下技能全览与使用说明（2026-03-09）**\n\n### 文档链接\nhttps://www.feishu.cn/docx/X7NMdndnIoyjmYx7Pe7cyuVFnhd\n\n### 群里发送结果\n已发送到 **思高乐教育群**\n消息 ID：\n`om_x100b55d3b0e56adcb214fd9a7d31b28`\n\n如果你要，本王下一步还能继续帮你做两种增强版：\n- **讲师版**：更适合对外介绍、分享、培训\n- **销售版**：更强调“能解决什么问题、适合什么人、能带来什么价值”\n\n你一句话，本王继续给你精修。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0e68f4bd2fc3c1440169ae7fe57b8c81919cdafe3252a237b9"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":168,"output":242,"cacheRead":235648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":236058,"cost":{"input":0.000294,"output":0.003388,"cacheRead":0.0412384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0449204}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773043682936}}
